com.rli.vds.util

Interface UserDefinedInterception


  • public interface UserDefinedInterception
    The interface to implements various LDAP operations like select, insert, update, delete and authenticate for the dvx node that it has been defined. The operations must be implemented in the corresponding functions. The src XMLOperation object in each function represents all the Meta information like Connection Stirng, Filter, Attributes, etc in XML format.
